Vivian Prescott https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vivian_Prescott 0 Vivian Prescott was an Italian born American actress. She appeared in 202 films between 1909 and 1917. She was born in Genoa, Italy and spent some time on the American stage before entering silent pictures. Vivian_Prescott was an_Italian_born_American_actress .
